    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a charm, so it's totally ready for your next adventure! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
